@mark
Did you check another app right before entering the last letter? Sometimes the app needs a second to sync back up with servers, or whatever it's doing, so if you come back from another application you need to wait like 5 seconds before finishing the puzzle.

I haven't found a solution to this problem other than clearing the puzzle and redoing it.

@Bill in Yokohama
(Haven't done that puzzle yet)
I would guess [Mo]="moment," SEC="second."

@Heidi
On the initial fill, the iPad app most definitely treated the picture squares as having been completed, skipping them during the fill. The only way I knew to go back and type over them was by coming here and seeing someone else figured it out. 

