@Heidi
After posting the above, I read more comments that said the Rebus button would reveal the letter behind the picture. I went back to the completed puzzle and did that. I found out that I had only entered letters for the top and middle pictures. The bottom one did not have a letter behind the picture, but I got the ‚Äúpuzzle completed‚Äù indication anyway.

